ive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.co.cygames.princessconnectredive&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=7808b77b\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.cygames.princessconnectredive</a><br />\nVPN攻略(日版only 台版無視就得)<br />\nopenvpn+vpn gate<br />\n用法:<br />\n1 安裝openvpn<br />\n2 上<a href=\"http://vpngate.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvpngate.net&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=11e2f122\" target=\"_blank\">http://vpngate.net</a>，搵server，下載openvpn配罝文件(有tcp同udp 2種，建議用udp比較快)<br />\n3 開openvpn apps，import返你下載既ovpn file就用得<br />\n<br />\n當然app store / play store上有其他一鍵vpn既apps，不過大多數都係超慢同斷線斷到仆街，所以識揀一定係揀vpngate<br />\n<br />\n台版<br />\nAPP STORE<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E8%B6%85%E7%95%B0%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90-re-dive/id1390473317?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B5%2590-re-dive%2Fid1390473317%3Fmt%3D8&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=6051ae63\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E8%B6%85%E7%95%B0%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90-re-dive/id1390473317?mt=8</a>   <br />\nGOOGLE PLAY<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tw.sonet.princessconnect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dtw.sonet.princessconnect&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=42775174\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tw.sonet.princessconnect</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>警惕世人</ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZXJGc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZXJGc0.png&h=7c1f63cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>Q&amp;A</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><br />\nQ: 自己首抽好定淘仔買AC好?<br />\nA: 想長玩就一定係買AC，不論係公會戰定PVP，有幾隻限係必需，但呢度都有唔少巴打係唔買咁玩，但預左會辛苦小小<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手台服應該去美食/真步/破曉？<br />\nA: 破曉&gt;&gt;&gt;真步&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;美食<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手應該打活動定衝rank?<br />\nA: 未到50lv 一定唔可以入活動任何一關 否則果期活動都唔會跌金裝<br />\n<br />\nQ: 係唔係d 角色愈升高星就愈勁?<br />\nA: 廢話!當然係,但有d角色打公會戰果陣,因為高星,所以防係高左,扣血少d慢d,出UB 既次數會反而少左,所以大部份輔助角都唔使升5星<br />\n<br />\n卡3星唔好升星系列:<br />\n優衣(新年)<br />\n靜流(情人節)<br />\n<del>泳裝咲戀?</del><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\nQ: 咁新手一開始要做咩?<br />\nA: 選一坦一補三輸出主力咁升，之後打主線，升到50lv如果有活動就入去活動升lv加打金裝，之後就係不停咁打主線，唔夠打就升角色RANK<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解我入唔到驚?<br />\nA: 因為要用VPN(日版only)<br />\n<br />\nQ:我到底打緊機定睇緊動畫？<br />\nA:問嚟做乜吖，Why not both<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔夠mana升技/升裝?<br />\nA: 用石換啦，1日10石就必換，有多就換到60石1pack先停<br />\n<br />\nQ: $有咩用?<br />\nA: 買公會小屋傢私,，優先升級會出道具嗰幾件<br />\n<br />\nQ:係咪得3星勁？<br />\nA:唔係，有好多二星都勁，例如宮子(布丁)/空花(抖M)/深月(抖S) (下面有圖)<br />\n<br />\nQ:係咪要抽先拎到角色？<br />\nA:只要有恆心，儲夠角色碎片都可以有<br />\n<br />\nQ:咩係角色碎片？<br />\nA:打hard/用地下城coin/抽重覆角拎嘅女神碎片去換嘅一樣道具<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點升角色星數?見3星再上有五星但抽唔到<br />\nA: 能力開花，角色碎片儲夠就升到星數<br />\n<br />\nQ:升3星係咪必要？<br />\nA:可以咁講，其一會有新圖，其二升到3星先開到絆lv上限，而你角色每升一個絆level 就會有新角色故事，睇完角色能力會上升同有石拎<br />\n<br />\nQ:有幾多種角色？<br />\nA:基本上為坦/中鋒/後防/魔法師/補師<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>首抽／買AC推薦</ins></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">封面推薦</span></em></ins><br />\n<strong><ins>台服</ins></strong><br />\n泳裝飯團<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEQTTZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEQTTZU.png&h=8a76fd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2ZNe3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2ZNe3X.jpg&h=e1537cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新年優衣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaHK0vB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaHK0vB.png&h=cfd24f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eoQ1jv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeoQ1jv2.jpg&h=b8eda2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情人姐姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PpLXG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PpLXG3.png&h=5a4c2705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGzF3wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGzF3wf.png&h=6ebffd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水著爆弓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEmFMCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEmFMCM.png&h=508e99f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0s2fxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0s2fxG.jpg&h=53c1b0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水著老師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbOg4pA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbOg4pA.png&h=b69cca12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFArHbi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFArHbi.png&h=fb5c8ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>-e個po有個傳說，搶1001開po同老婆示愛，就會中限-</strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老婆示愛區</span></ins><br />\n自己搵圖啦"},{"pid":"96d4638fb08fadee4abcb1dda0b69726fc04e2b6","tid":1971380,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:56:11.000Z","msg":"大翅膀"},{"pid":"5bbcffd86b8f0a91d5777c633feb819fe6ec3c76","tid":1971380,"uid":10103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"唔小心1001左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下點解次次P